Fill ObjectFileBase::s_object_files_ with all loaded object files, including later added shared libraries loaded with dlopen. For this libelf (maybe libdw?) has to be used in the current "best practise" way. The important part here is to look up information on the internet about how to do this today, without looking at the (old) dwarf.cc file of which we do not know if that is doing things correctly or in the "best practise" way.
